{"tid":2159884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（港台已跪）港台訪羅冠聰節目下架　梁家榮內部解說：不可成傳播反國安法平台","createTime":"2020-08-16T15:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:54:25.000Z","uid":333488,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"50416237ca182c4eae6ff94d0eb557b10da6ff2c","tid":2159884,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"香港電台7月31日播放特備直播節目《2020立法會選舉延後之戰》，並訪問曾宣布參選立法會的前香港眾志主席羅冠聰，但及後該節目下架，無法在港台網頁及YouTube頻道重溫。<br />\n港台機構傳訊及節目標準總監伍曼儀回覆查詢時承認，廣播處長梁家榮早前曾在恆常節目會議上回應質疑，對涉及違反國安法的事項要審慎處理，港台作為媒體及公共廣播機構，不應該作為平台，讓涉違反港區國安法的人傳播有關主張。<br />\n伍曼儀強調下架是管理層編採決定，認為在涉及國安法的事件宜審慎處理。<br />\n<br />\n連港台都跪埋⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea6b33e6e60a977603ab4746d6037555cd2e587","tid":2159884,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:06:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf0f9bd601251eef8c4505ca12ec273812d8d36f","tid":2159884,"uid":118217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"自我審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43c8197e90a82c6eb819d21bed87d0efdfe65b5","tid":2159884,"uid":118217,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fea6b33e6e60a977603ab4746d6037555cd2e587","tid":2159884,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:06:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"咁都唔叫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e470172a3ed2b04cdb31c1dced0b88e0c47bd91a","tid":2159884,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"別怪他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fa57331c4c54609b621aad62a56fb81d037dfc","tid":2159884,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50416237ca182c4eae6ff94d0eb557b10da6ff2c","tid":2159884,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,